&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Crofton and Sharlston Medical Practice&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Part time medical receptionist required&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are offering an exciting opportunity for a part-time receptionist, to join a well-organised two site GP practice. We are in a semi-rural area near Wakefield with good motorway links to surrounding areas. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The position is for approximately 20 hours per week but may also include some early morning and / or late nights on a rota basis. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Your rate of pay will be dependent on experience and what you can bring to the role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Must be a good team player with excellent computer skills, self-motivated and have a &lt;span&gt;polite manner and flexible approach along with being willing to cover colleagues holiday or sickness if required. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Previous experience of working in a GP practice or having excellent customer service skills would be advantageous but not essential &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Having your own transport is desirable as the practice works over two sites and you will be expected to work at either site as per your rota and also covering colleagues when on holiday or unable to work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you would like to be considered for this position, please submit your CV for the attention of the Practice Manager, Ann Batty&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please be aware this job advert will close when sufficient applications have been received&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
